column5: Not me, A green Heron.  Saw this video and thought it was pretty cool.  Didn't know they did that.  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uBuPiC3ArL8#t=1
Who ever coined the phrase "dumb animals"?
Great video!!,they are sure smarter then we are sometimes lol.

Thats amazing. It seemed like charity first as the bird was getting back less and less bread but it knew what it was doing. I guess I know what to bring out if I only have minimal live bait left. Thanks for sharing
